OL,3,CBrothers will not face third airport
OL,4,Cassault trial
OL,6,FTwo brothers accused of assaulting a
OL,7,Fpolice officer at Manchester Airport
OL,8,Fduring a fracas which went viral on
OL,9,Fsocial media will not face a third
OL,10,Ftrial after prosecutors offered no
OL,11,Fevidence.
OL,13,FTwo separate juries at Liverpool Crown
OL,14,FCourt failed to reach verdicts on
OL,15,Fallegations that Mohammed Fahir Amaaz,
OL,16,F21, and Muhammad Amaad, 26, assaulted
OL,17,FPC Zachary Marsden in July 2024
OL,18,Fcausing him actual bodily harm.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
