CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1780089066
OL,3,CBrothers will not face third airport
OL,4,Cassault trial
OL,6,FBoth men, from Rochdale, Greater
OL,7,FManchester, denied the charge and said
OL,8,Fthey acted in lawful self-defence, or
OL,9,Fin defence of the other.
OL,11,FThe second jury was discharged on 21
OL,12,FMay after they deliberated for nearly
OL,13,F20 hours following a five-week trial.
OL,15,FAmaaz was remanded in custody in 2025
OL,16,Fafter he was convicted at the first
OL,17,Ftrial of the assault of PC Lydia Ward
OL,18,Fand PC Ellie Cook during the same
OL,19,Fincident on 23 July.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
