OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1780089066
OL,3,CBrothers will not face third airport
OL,4,Cassault trial
OL,6,FThe court heard the three Greater
OL,7,FManchester Police officers entered the
OL,8,FTerminal 2 car park paystation after
OL,9,Freports that a male fitting Amaaz's
OL,10,Fdescription had headbutted a member of
OL,11,Fthe public at a Starbucks cafe in the
OL,12,Fairport minutes earlier.
OL,14,FThe prosecution said Amaaz resisted
OL,15,Ftheir attempts to take him outside and
OL,16,FAmaad then intervened.
OL,18,FBut the brothers, from Rochdale,
OL,19,FGreater Manchester, said their actions
OL,20,Fwere defensive rather than offensive
OL,21,Fas they said they came "under attack".
OL,26,@}D@XOU}D@eO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
